d to measure the causal effect of an advertising campaign for a consumer\nproduct sold at stores of a large national retail chain.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 19 Jan 2018 03:14:48 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 1 Mar 2018 02:24:47 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 12 Mar 2018 17:38:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-03-13"}
